result.adr_address: 29 Cheung Ning St, To Kwa Wan, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 29 Cheung Ning St, To Kwa Wan, Hong Kong
result.name: Chez Louis Restaurant

reviews.text:
Surprise! Surprise!
Wonderful Master Chef Louis who has a lot of experience from the world and he cooked the food with passion!   All the food are very delicious.
Excellent and attentive customer services with warm and friendly smiles.  Amazing team!  The manager and the lady boss are very nice!
Really enjoy all the fresh seafood, don’t miss the mussels, fresh crab 🦀 to share as a starter and delicious grill salmon. The steak is so tender and cook perfectly.  All the main dishes are come with the chunky chips and signature sauce. It’s really yummy. 
My family and I are definitely come back soon. 
Thank you Master Chef Louis and the excellent team!  Keep it up!🥰🥰

I stayed in Hong Kong for 4 days..but this was definitely the best restaurant I tried.
I own a restaurant in Italy, I am very used to eat good food, but Louis the chef put all his heart to make amazing dishes, I really enjoyed my dinner There. 
If you have time Guys and you want spend a couple of good hours eating a good food this is the place.
First time in this restaurant. Ordered some ordinary dishes, fish and chips and seafood risotto. Both above expectations. Will come back to try more signature dishes.

What a great find! Chef Louis is fantastic, the restaurant has a nice summer-day vibe, good beers, and his staff are friendly and approachable. Food is delicious and a good portion. Thanks for having us!
Great food, great prices and great service. A difficult trifecta to find in Hong Kong!
